lightstep-tracer-cpp
------------------------------------------
LightStep distributed tracing library for C++

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.0.7-1
  libcares2-1.14.0-1
  libevent2.0_5-2.0.22-1
  libgcc1-7.4.0-1
  liblightstep_tracer-devel-0.10.0-1bl1
  liblightstep_tracer0-0.10.0-1bl1
  libopentracing1-1.5.1-1bl1
  libprotobuf18-3.7.1-1
  libstdc++6-7.4.0-1
  pkg-config-1.6.0-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.29-1
  cmake-3.13.1-1
  cygport-0.33.1-1
  gcc-core-7.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-7.4.0-1
  libprotobuf-devel-3.7.1-1
  ninja-1.9.0-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/lightstep/lightstep-tracer-cpp

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/lightstep/lightstep-tracer-cpp/archive/v0.10.0.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack lightstep-tracer-cpp-0.10.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./lightstep-tracer-cpp-0.10.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/lightstep-tracer-cpp-0.10.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/lightstep-tracer-cpp-0.10.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/liblightstep_tracer0-0.10.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/liblightstep_tracer-devel-0.10.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(lightstep-tracer-cpp)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/lightstep-tracer-cpp.README
  /usr/share/doc/lightstep-tracer-cpp/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/lightstep-tracer-cpp/README.md

(liblightstep_tracer0)
  /usr/bin/cyglightstep_tracer-0.dll

(liblightstep_tracer-devel)
  /usr/include/lightstep/binary_carrier.h
  /usr/include/lightstep/metrics_observer.h
  /usr/include/lightstep/tracer.h
  /usr/include/lightstep/transporter.h
  /usr/include/lightstep/version.h
  /usr/lib/liblightstep_tracer.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/lightstep-tracer-cpp.pc

------------------

